<h2>GriefShare</h2><p class="eventtime">Every Sunday, from 09/09/2012 to 11/25/2012<span class='event-sep'>, </span><span class="eventTime"> 9:00 AM - 10:15 AM</span></p><br/><b>Group:</b> Life Learning<br/><b>Cost:</b> $0.00</p><p><b>Coordinator:</b> Joel Slater</p><!-- Joel Slater --><div id="text"><p><span>GriefShare is a 13-week support group for people dealing with the death of a loved one. Every session is "self-contained" so attendees are welcome to join at any point in the series. This series is designed to help you successfully travel the journey from mourning to joy. Workshop fee is $25 per participant, and is facilitated by Tom Dooley.</span></p>
